TitleEnglish: Mahou Tsukai Pretty Cure! The Movie: Miraculous Transformation! Cure Mofurun
SummaryEnglish: Mahou Tsukai Pretty Cure! The Movie: Miraculous Transformation! Cure Mofurun! (映画魔法つかいプリキュア！奇跡の変身！キュアモフルン！, Mahou Tsukai Pretty Cure! The Movie: Miraculous Transformation! Cure Mofurun!?) is the 21stPretty Cure movie produced by Toei Animation. The movie was released in Japanese cinemas on October 29th, 2016. The movie was released on DVD and Blu-ray on March 1st, 2017.
Aliases: Eiga Mahō Tsukai Purikyua! Kiseki no Henshin! Kyua Mofurun!
